    </li>
  <li>Hit the upload button and select the extension zip file and upload it<br>
    </li>
  <li>Enable the extension then click on it's title to go to the extension settings<br>
    </li>
  <li>Once you have configured your IEM database connection and all required settings you can then create an import<br>
